The paper discusses a method of exploratory data analysis using clustering and visualization, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new clustering algorithm (alpha-clustering) and applies the method to biological data, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
